In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Barton NACHAMIE. No. D-2931. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 11, 2016.

Barton Nachamie, of New York, New York, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
